---

This is my attempt at CompactInstall, a replacement for Install3.x. 
With this floppy disk image you are able to quickly setup your new big hard
drive without involving your current system. Maximum space that can be used
is 127 GiB or only 8 GiB if your Miggy lacks MMU.

---

